I"Ó<ol>
  <li>Shutdown all running VMs:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>vim-cmd vmsvc/power.shutdown <span class="sb">`</span>vim-cmd vmsvc/getallvms | <span class="nb">awk</span> <span class="s1">'NR&gt;1 {print $1}'</span><span class="sb">`</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Enter <em>maintenance mode</em>:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>esxcli system maintenanceMode <span class="nb">set</span> <span class="nt">-e</span> <span class="nb">true</span> <span class="nt">-t</span> 0
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Shutdown ESXi:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>esxcli system shutdown poweroff <span class="nt">-d</span> 10 <span class="nt">-r</span> <span class="s2">"Graceful Shutdown"</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Exit <em>maintenance mode</em>:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>esxcli system maintenanceMode <span class="nb">set</span> <span class="nt">-e</span> <span class="nb">false</span> <span class="nt">-t</span> 0
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

